Class MMPresetGroupRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.embl.rieslab.emu.micromanager.presetgroups.MMPresetGroupRegistry

extends java.lang.Object
    Class holding a HashMap of the MMPresetGroups and their name as displayed in the current Micro-manager session.
    Author:
    Joran Deschamps

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructor and Description
      MMPresetGroupRegistry(mmcorej.CMMCore core, MMPropertiesRegistry mmpropReg)
      The constructor receives the current Micro-manager core instance and extracts all the preset groups, building a HashMap of the MMPresetGroup indexed by the group name.
